<div id="kopijbody">
  <h2>Perl workshop</h2>
  <p>
  The Perl Workshop is a day of presentations and encounters by and for Perl users with interesting content for new and existing users of the Perl programming language.
  </p>
  <p>
  <h3>Change of date and venue</h3>
  <p>
  Unfortunately we had to make changes to the planning of the workshop. If you've seen an earlier announcement for a workshop in May, please ignore that. Apologies for any inconvenience.
  </p>
  <h3>Updates to follow soon</h3>
  <p>
  This is just to inform you about the date and venue. We're planning to have a website with full details ready by the end of the first week of April.
  </p>
</div> <!-- kopijbody -->
  
<div id="sidebar">
  <h2>Organizers</h2>
  
  <p>
  The Dutch Perl Workshop is organized by the <a href="http://perl.nl/sppn">Stichting Perl Promotie Nederland</a>.
  </p>
  
  <p>
  To find out more about Dutch Perl workshops, please check out the websites of our workshops in <a href="http://www.perlworkshop.nl/nlpw2016">2016</a> and <a href="http://www.perlworkshop.nl/nlpw2016/conferences_nl.html">previous years</a>.
  </p>
  
</div> <!-- sidebar -->

